OL,5, Pope Francis has condemned human       
OL,6, "hunger for wealth and power" at       
OL,7, Christmas Eve Mass in the Vatican,     
OL,8, seemingly referring to the war in      
OL,9, Ukraine and other conflicts.           
OL,11,F"How many wars have we seen!" he said, 
OL,12,Fadding that the main victims were "the 
OL,13,Fweak and the vulnerable".              
OL,15,F"I think above all of the children     
OL,16,Fdevoured by war, poverty and           
OL,17,Finjustice," the pontiff added.         
OL,19,FHe was addressing worshippers at St    
OL,20,FPeter's Basilica in Vatican City.      
